title: DDFP 502: Week 8 recap, Jamie Collins trade & Midseason Awards
itunes:title: DDFP 502: Week 8 recap, Jamie Collins trade & Midseason Awards
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor and longtime friend of the show, Ross Tucker, to discuss the midseason MVP, the second best team in the NFL and how Andre Johnson stacks up against Tim Brown, A.J. Green and Calvin Johnson. Also, the fellas break down the trade of Jamie Collins to the Cleveland Browns and whether or not it was the right move for the Patriots. Then, Shek and Ike are joined by the "Fantasy Hipsters" Matt Harmon and Matt Franciscovich to discuss the best wins and worst losses from Week 8, highlighting the Falcons' win and the Eagles' loss. Plus, Shek reveals his midseason AFC & NFC playoff pro-shektions!
